Package com.sicomsa.dmt

Class VerificaResponse.Builder

java.lang.Object
com.sicomsa.dmt.VerificaResponse.Builder
Enclosing class:
VerificaResponse
public static class VerificaResponse.Builder extends Object
Utility class to facilitate creation of VerificaResponse instances.

Contains methods to set parameters and the build VerificaResponses instances with the build method.

The build method does not clear any parameters and lets you reuse the builder setting or resetting parameters. You can reset all the parameters with the clear method.
